      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="401C64FJ">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="italics">By Dr</hi>. Swift.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">The following verses were communicated to us, in manuscript, by a correspondent, who knows not whether they were ever made public; but from their not being inserted in the dean's works, believes they were not. Be that as it may, the reader, we presume, will not think them unworthy of a place in this magazine.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-401C64FJ-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-401C64FJ-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">Y</hi>OUR mould'ring walls are mending still,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-401C64FJ-line-2" n="2">Your churches in neglect lye;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401C64FJ-line-3" n="3">But yet, the scripture you fulfil,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-401C64FJ-line-4" n="4">By walking circumspectly.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401C64FJ-line-5" n="5"><lb/>The church and clergy here, no doubt,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-401C64FJ-line-6" n="6">Are very much a-kin,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401C64FJ-line-7" n="7">Both weather-beaten are without,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-401C64FJ-line-8" n="8">Both empty are within.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
